have option to create a big center but now this dark-squared Bishop is away
from g7 square and the King can easily get in the trouble.} (13... Bg7 14. c4
$14 {Now White has great center and more space and his position is better.})
14. O-O (14. c4 $4 Ba5 $19) 14... exd5 15. exd5 Ba5 16. f5 $5 $13 {White has
